*gnome-applets-1.4.0.4-r2 (28 Jun 2002)
  28 Jun 2002 ; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> gnome-applets-1.4.0.4-r2.ebuild :
  changed the dependency from gnome-core to gnome-panel
  since core and panel are the same package, same binaries and same files, there shouldn't be any conflicts at any time. 

